<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style type="text/css" media="screen">
      body { width: 600px; }
      .quick-links { margin-top: 50px; }
      .salutation { margin-bottom: 50px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <p class="salutation">
        Hi <%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %>,
      </p>
      <p>
        You have been scheduled for an interview for <%= link_to @job_application.job_posting.job.title, @job_application.job_posting.job %>, for <%= link_to @job_application.job_posting.job.organization.name, @job_application.job_posting.job.organization %>.
      </p>
      <p>
        The interview is scheduled at the following time:
        <br>
        <em>
          <%= @job_application.interview.start_time.strftime("%A, %d %b at %l:%M %p") %> to <%= @job_application.interview.end_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %>.
        </em>
      </p>
      <br>
      <p>
        Please watch for a follow up email shortly with information about how your interview will be conducted. If you don't recieve it within 12 hours of this email, please reach out to your interview panel chair at <%= mail_to @job_application.job_posting.job.organization.email %> for instructions.
      </p>
      <p>
        Otherwise, no further action is needed from you to confirm the interview. You can view all your interviews at <%= link_to "my job applications", user_job_applications_url %>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Best of luck on your interview!
      </p>
      <p>
        <i>Please note that all EngSoc hiring is done according to EngSoc Hiring Policy as seen in Section Gamma of the EngSoc Policy Manual available on our website under "About - Government - Governing Documents".</i>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-links">
      <h3>Quick links</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><%= link_to "EngSoc Dash", root_url %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "My Job Applications", user_job_applications_url %></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <%= render 'shared/mail/footer' %>
  </body>
</html>
